name: The Remix of the Remix of a Misunderstanding of Rarity Driven By Speculative Capitalists Dressed In Sheep's Clothing pt6
description: "I'll stay in here until you're starving, until you understand you can trust me, that I give to you unconditionally, out of the purest love", claimed the PFP. "I'll stay here until this cage becomes a place of peace, of pleasure-not torment. I will stay in here until you can't resist me."
